    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "FLIGHTTIMES\nand News of the Port\nSan Diego International Airport\nLindbergh Field\nJune 1, 1997\nstel\nThe largest cruise ship to visit San Diego, CELEBRITY\nCRUISES' new, 1,870-passenger GALAXY recently made\na port-of call here. The 77,713-ton vessel is one of three\nships operated by CELEBRITY CRUISES that will dock at\nthe CRUISE SHIP TERMINAL this year.\nSchedule Information Contained Herein\nIs Subject To Change By The Airlines.\nPlease Consult Your Airline\nFor Further Information."
